Qe4 $17) 15... b5 $5 16. Qa6 b4 (16... Rb8 $5 17. Bf4 Qb6 (17... Rb6 18. Qxa7 {
[%cal Rf4c7]}) 18. Qxb6 Rxb6 19. Bc7 b4 20. Bxb6 bxc3 21. bxc3 Nxe2+ 22. Kf1
Nxc3 23. Rd3 axb6 24. Rxc3 $11 {_|_}) 17. Nd5 Nxd5 18. Bxd5 Rb8 19. Bf4 Qb6 20.
Qc4 $44 d6 21. e3 Nb5 {[%csl Rf4]} 22. g4 Nc7 23. Be4 g6 24. Rd2 Rbd8 25. Qe2
$6 (25. Rad1 $44 {was more accurate.}) 25... d5 $1 {Giving back a pawn but
lifting the blockade.} 26. Bxc7 ({After} 26. Bxc7 Qxc7 27. Rxd5 (27. Bxd5 c4)
27... c4 {it is Black who can play for a win but he was satisfied with a draw.}
) 1/2-1/2

